_:Nb57fd072676d496f9334b0e58bff97f2 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Andy became Chief Digital Information Officer for Building Digital UK (BDUK), at the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology (DSIT) in January 2026.</p>\n\n<p>He is responsible for the use of technology, data and digital services including internal business transformation and the professional oversight of technology standards. </p>\n\n<p>Andy joined BDUK in 2022 as Head of Technical Operations, leading the management of technical input for the Open Market Review.                                     </p>\n\n<p>He previously worked in the private sector, including fifteen years at Openreach in leadership and operational roles. This included delivering key regional connectivity programmes.</p>\n" .
